Entry.JapaneseText: お客さんだ。静かにしてろよ？
戦争で親を亡くした子どもたちだ。 オレが引き取って面倒みてる
Entry.EnglishText: These kids lost their parents in the war... So I decided to take care of them myself.

Entry.JapaneseText: ミリー、お客さんが来たときは どうするんだ？
Entry.EnglishText: Milly, how do we greet our guests?

Entry.JapaneseText: グリッド、ジョンに 飯の支度を してやってくれ

Entry.EnglishText: Is it okay to use fire?

Entry.JapaneseText: ああ、オレもいるしな。 なにかあったら呼ぶんだぞ
Entry.EnglishText: Yeah. I'll be around here. If anything happens just gimme a shout.

Entry.JapaneseText: さてと。なんだっけ、<CLE>と <MIN>に会いに来たんだったか
Entry.EnglishText: With that out of the way... Why was it you came here to meet with <CLE> and <MIN>?

Entry.JapaneseText: うん、えっと…… 何から話せばいいかな？
Entry.EnglishText: Yeah, huh... Where should we start from?

Entry.JapaneseText: なるほど…… マクスウェルってことは、 <Red>モーリア坑道<White>だな
Entry.EnglishText: So that's that... To meet Maxwell you'll need to go to the Morlia Mineshaft.

Entry.JapaneseText: よし、オレが一緒に 行ってやるよ
Entry.EnglishText: It's decided, I'll go with you guys.

Entry.JapaneseText: でも<CST>さんも 忙しいんじゃねーの？
……ああ、オレは <CLE>や<MIN>とは 違うんだ
ちょっと言い方がキツいせいで 周りから『コワいヤツ』って 思われてるみたいだしな
Entry.EnglishText: Maybe I'm trying too hard to pull the tough act. It's all thanks that someone told me I was "too weak" a long time ago.

Entry.JapaneseText: でもさ、 あの子どもたちには したわれてんだろ？
Entry.EnglishText: But, can you really leave these kids behind?

Entry.JapaneseText: 兄ちゃん！ どこ行くんだ！？
Entry.EnglishText: Big brother! Are you going somewhere!?

Entry.JapaneseText: ああ、ちょっとそこまでな。 おとなしく留守番してろよ
Entry.EnglishText: Yup, I'll be out for a bit. You guys take care of everything here, okay?

Entry.JapaneseText: ジョン、食いすぎて腹壊すなよ。 ミリー、寝る前には歯磨きだぞ
Entry.EnglishText: John, don't eat so much or you'll get stomach ache! Milly, brush your teeth before going to bed!

Entry.JapaneseText: グリッド、 ふたりのこと頼んだぞ
Entry.EnglishText: Grid, I leave these two on your care.
A-are you sure about this, Mister <CST>?

Entry.JapaneseText: ああ、道場の連中も親切で、 面倒見てくれてるからな
Entry.EnglishText: Sure. The Dojo's trainees will also take care of things here.

Entry.JapaneseText: それから、 『さん』はいらないぜ
Entry.EnglishText: Oh, and drop the whole "Mister" thing.

Entry.JapaneseText: わかった！ よろしくな、 <CST>
Entry.EnglishText: Right, then! Nice to have you around, <CST>!
